<div id="content_inner">
	<div class="other_center">
		<div class="gray_head_box">
			<div class="gray_head_heading"><h1>How to order?</h1></div>
		</div>

		<div class="location_view">            

			<h3>
				1. You want to order with Top Menu? It's easy.
			</h3>
			<p>
                Enter your postal code on the home page. The first 3 characters are enough then click on "GO !" and you will find the list for all the restaurants that delivers to you.
			</p>
			<h3>
				2. Feeling peckish for something special? No problems
			</h3>
			<p>
                You can choose the cuisine type that makes you happy by selecting it from the list on your left.
			</p>
			<h3>
				3. You found a restaurant?
			</h3>
			<ul>
				<li>
                    That delivers in <strong>Plateau, Villeray, Centre-Sud, Rosemont, Hochelaga, Outremont or Centre-Ville Est.</strong>
				</li>
			</ul>
			<p>
                Choose the dishes you like. When you choose a dish a pop up appears so you can choose the quantity and any options available for this dish. By clicking "ok" your selection is added to your basket.				
			</p>
			<ul>
				<li>
                    For all the other sectors you can read the PDF menu of the restaurant and then communicate directly with the restaurant.
				</li>
			</ul>
			<h3>
                4. Ready to order? Let's do it!				
			</h3>
			<p>
                Once your order finish you will need to:
			</p>
			<ul>
                <li>
                    Connect or create your Top Menu account
				</li>
				<li>
                    Confirm your order
				</li>
				<li>
                    To choose between delivery and pick-up
				</li>
                <li>
                    Enter your credit card information or choose to pay at the door
                </li>
                <li>
                    Click proceed to payment
                </li>
			</ul>
			
			<h3>
                5. What happens when you order is sent?
			</h3>
			<p>
                Once the order done, it's sent to the restaurant which will shortly respond to you, on the web page, the expected delivery time.
			</p>
			<p>
				If for some reason the restaurants declines the order your payment will not go through.
			</p>
			<p>
                You will receive an email to confirm your order
			</p>
            <br/>
			<p>
                Don't forget to tip the driver.
			</p>
		</div>
	</div>
</div>
